column2: Waitr Holdings, Inc. engages in an on-demand food ordering and delivery business. The company is headquartered in Lake Charles, Louisiana and currently employs 22,000 full-time employees. The companyâ€™s platform connects local restaurants to diners in the southeast United States. Its platform allows users to discover, order and receive food from local restaurants and national chains. As of September 30, 2018, it had over 7,700 restaurant partners in over 235 cities in the Southeast United States.
